summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property in Blocks 6 and 7, Terry's 5th Addition, Blocks 4 and 9, Plummer's Addition and Block 213, Seattle Tidelands for the expansion of existing city shop and storage facilities under Ordinance 91851, King County Cause No. 611775; accepting a certain condemnation award and making a reimbursable appropriation from the City Street Fund therefor.
